{"id":24,"parent_id":1,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":24,"title":"Genesis 23","subtitle":"","short_title":"Gen.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 23"],[".studySummary",["i","Sarah dies and is buried in the cave of Machpelah, which Abraham buys from Ephron the Hittite."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.1","order":"02.02.023.2096"},["b","1"],"And Sarah was an hundred and seven and twenty years old:",["i","these were"],"the years of the life of Sarah."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.2","order":"02.02.023.2097"},["b","2"],"And Sarah",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"died"],"in Kirjath-arba; the same",["i","is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"Hebron"],"in the land of Canaan: and Abraham came to mourn for Sarah, and to weep for her."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.3","order":"02.02.023.2098"},["b","3"],"¶And Abraham stood up from before his dead, and spake unto the sons of Heth, saying,"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.4","order":"02.02.023.2099"},["b","4"],"I",["i","am"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"a stranger"],"and a sojourner with you: give me a possession of a buryingplace with you, that I may bury my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"dead"],"out of my sight."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.5","order":"02.02.023.2100"},["b","5"],"And the children of Heth answered Abraham, saying unto him,"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.6","order":"02.02.023.2101"},["b","6"],"Hear us, my lord: thou",["i","art"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"a mighty prince"],"among us: in the choice of our sepulchres bury thy dead; none of us shall withhold from thee his sepulchre, but that thou mayest bury thy dead."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.7","order":"02.02.023.2102"},["b","7"],"And Abraham stood up, and bowed himself to the people of the land,",["i","even"],"to the children of Heth."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.8","order":"02.02.023.2103"},["b","8"],"And he communed with them, saying, If it be your mind that I should bury my dead out of my sight; hear me, and entreat for me to Ephron the son of Zohar,"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.9","order":"02.02.023.2104"},["b","9"],"That he may give me the cave of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Machpelah"],", which he hath, which",["i","is"],"in the end of his field; for as much money as it is worth he shall give it me for a possession of a buryingplace amongst you."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.10","order":"02.02.023.2105"},["b","10"],"And Ephron dwelt among the children of Heth: and Ephron the Hittite answered Abraham in the audience of the children of Heth,",["i","even"],"of all that went in at the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"gate"],"of his city, saying,"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.11","order":"02.02.023.2106"},["b","11"],"Nay, my lord, hear me: the field give I thee, and the cave that",["i","is"],"therein, I give it thee; in the presence of the sons of my people give I it thee: bury thy dead."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.12","order":"02.02.023.2107"},["b","12"],"And Abraham bowed down himself before the people of the land."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.13","order":"02.02.023.2108"},["b","13"],"And he spake unto Ephron in the audience of the people of the land, saying, But if thou",["i","wilt give it,"],"I pray thee, hear me: I will give thee money for the field; take",["i","it"],"of me, and I will bury my dead there."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.14","order":"02.02.023.2109"},["b","14"],"And Ephron answered Abraham, saying unto him,"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.15","order":"02.02.023.2110"},["b","15"],"My lord, hearken unto me: the land",["i","is worth"],"four hundred",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"shekels"],"of silver; what",["i","is"],"that betwixt me and thee? bury therefore thy dead."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.16","order":"02.02.023.2111"},["b","16"],"And Abraham hearkened unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Ephron"],"; and Abraham",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"weighed"],"to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"Ephron"],"the silver, which he had named in the audience of the sons of Heth, four hundred shekels of silver, current",["i","money"],"with the merchant."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.17","order":"02.02.023.2112"},["b","17"],"¶And the field of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Ephron"],", which",["i","was"],"in Machpelah, which",["i","was"],"before Mamre, the field, and the cave which",["i","was"],"therein, and all the trees that",["i","were"],"in the field, that",["i","were"],"in all the borders round about, were made sure"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.18","order":"02.02.023.2113"},["b","18"],"Unto Abraham for a possession in the presence of the children of Heth, before all that went in at the gate of his city."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.19","order":"02.02.023.2114"},["b","19"],"And after this, Abraham buried Sarah his wife in the cave of the field of Machpelah before Mamre: the same",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Hebron"],"in the land of Canaan."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.20","order":"02.02.023.2115"},["b","20"],"And the field, and the cave that",["i","is"],"therein, were made sure unto Abraham for a possession of a buryingplace by the sons of Heth."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.2a","order":"02.02.023.2116"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/24.67"},"Gen. 24:67"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.2b","order":"02.02.023.2118"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/13.18"},"Gen. 13:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.19"},"23:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.4a","order":"02.02.023.2120"},["b","4a"],["span.small","IE"],"a resident alien.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stranger"},"TG Stranger"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.4b","order":"02.02.023.2122"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/death"},"TG Death"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.6a","order":"02.02.023.2124"},["b","6a"],["span.small","HEB"],"a prince of God."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.9a","order":"02.02.023.2126"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/25.9"},"Gen. 25:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/49.30"},"49:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.10a","order":"02.02.023.2128"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/34.20"},"Gen. 34:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ruth/4.1"},"Ruth 4:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.15a","order":"02.02.023.2130"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/30.13"},"Ex. 30:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/45.12"},"Ezek. 45:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.16a","order":"02.02.023.2132"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/49.30"},"Gen. 49:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.16b","order":"02.02.023.2134"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/21.25"},"1 Chr. 21:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/32.9"},"Jer. 32:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.16c","order":"02.02.023.2136"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/25.10"},"Gen. 25:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.17a","order":"02.02.023.2138"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/50.13"},"Gen. 50:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.16"},"Acts 7:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.19a","order":"02.02.023.2140"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/23.2"},"Gen. 23:2"],"."]]}
